United States Court of Appeals Fifth Circuit. Dec. 21, 1967. John A. Nelson, St. Petersburg, Fla., for appellant. Charles M. Roberts, Frank B. Watson, Jr., Roberts, Watson, Taylor & Friday, Fort Myers, Fla., for appellee Hartford Accident & Indemnity Co. of Hartford, Conn. *953James A.
